Text.Value: How can I get to Moonrise Towers?
Find... path to temple... orders of General...
*The corpse does not stir. It will answer no more questions.*

EditorData.NodeContext: The tunnel has all kinds of ominous sounds coming out of it so Nere can't be sure it's safe.

Text.Value: *The spell's power wanes. You can ask no more questions.*
Tell me more about this General.
Did you come here with the duergar?
What about this temple is so important?

Synopsis: Speak with Dead dialogue for True Soul Nere. He may tell you about the temple he was looking for as well as what is inside it.
